title: RedCrab 6.1.1 Portable
description:
Advanced Scientific Calculator



Download, unzip and use.  It is portable and free.  Enjoy!




RedCrab is a scientific, statistics and financial calculation program with a full screen formula editor.
The mathematical expressions can be entered in an editor window similar to a virtual piece of paper.
RedCrab supports the entry of complex algebraic equations like fractions, square roots, exponents, variables etc. for technical and scientific applications.
